                        <interp inst="t18500506-name-224" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. These are both counterfeit, and from the same mould.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I gave her a good sixpence; I should not have taken the shilling back, only I saw she had a bad sixpence in the till, which I thought she would have given me.</p>
